summary: #DJFatChip Joins Pin Clubs ♡ ↪ Not all the Ghost Pokemon will be “spooky” to me. Some are just too beautiful and elegant to...
caption:
#DJFatChip Joins Pin Clubs ♡
↪ Not all the Ghost Pokemon will be “spooky” to me. Some are just too beautiful and elegant to not take cute pictures of them in the sun, and Misdreavus is one of those lovely Ghost Type Pokemon that I just see enjoying sleeping in nature waiting for nightfall! ♡ (Even if it’s often found in caves :P). This is January 2019′s pin and is one (1) of nine (9) other Ghost Pokemon that you can choose from depending on your tier! Check out this amazing Patreon Pin Club!

Join Sam’s Pokemon pin club! ➡️https://www.patreon.com/pokemonpins
